00:10:11.220 --> 00:10:13.740
is the number of photons
which arrive during the time

00:10:13.740 --> 00:10:15.160
constant.

00:10:15.160 --> 00:10:16.710
So that's sort of the mapping.

00:10:16.710 --> 00:10:18.770
