00:40:24.000 --> 00:40:26.240
So this was i1.

00:40:29.260 --> 00:40:36.450
If I would now look at--
let me change the color--

00:40:36.450 --> 00:40:42.340
at the current, i2, the only
anything which changes is

00:40:42.340 --> 00:40:47.260
that because the quantum
noise is transmitted

00:40:47.260 --> 00:40:50.070
with a positive
coefficient, that I

00:40:50.070 --> 00:40:53.460
have to put a plus sign here.

00:40:53.460 --> 00:40:56.390
And now, you realize the magic.

00:40:56.390 --> 00:41:01.510
When you form i1
plus i2, whatever

00:41:01.510 --> 00:41:04.430
came through the vacuum part,
or through the open part,

00:41:04.430 --> 00:41:06.430
cancels out.

00:41:06.430 --> 00:41:09.990
Therefore, when we calculated--
or when I asked you

00:41:09.990 --> 00:41:13.060
for the variance
in i1 plus i2, it

00:41:13.060 --> 00:41:15.990
was independent, whether
there was squeezing,

00:41:15.990 --> 00:41:18.530
whether whatever was
at the vacuum part.

00:41:18.530 --> 00:41:23.680
And therefore, it doesn't matter
whether I put my power meter,

00:41:23.680 --> 00:41:26.220
measuring both currents--
both beams-- before the beam

00:41:26.220 --> 00:41:27.720
splitter or after
the beam splitter.

00:41:31.050 --> 00:41:32.630
But-- yes, a question?

