00:42:47.228 --> 00:42:49.036
AUDIENCE: --If a's will cancel.

00:42:49.036 --> 00:42:50.510
PROFESSOR: Oh.

00:42:50.510 --> 00:42:52.680
It is clear that
in i1-- OK, yes.

00:42:52.680 --> 00:42:56.052
But the question
is whether we have

00:42:56.052 --> 00:43:00.120
to perform i1 minus
i2 or i1 plus i2.

00:43:00.120 --> 00:43:01.780
Well, I don't know
