00:44:40.850 --> 00:44:46.432
Now, we want to talk about
the displaced squeezed vacuum.

00:44:46.432 --> 00:44:48.510
Now, we put everything together.

00:44:48.510 --> 00:44:50.970
Remember, we have
learned by applying

00:44:50.970 --> 00:44:54.520
the squeezing operator, how
we can squeeze the vacuum.

00:44:54.520 --> 00:44:56.740
And then, with the
displacement operator,

00:44:56.740 --> 00:45:01.370
I can move the displaced vacuum,
that there is an expectation

00:45:01.370 --> 00:45:04.450
value, alpha, for the field.

00:45:04.450 --> 00:45:09.070
So it now looks like a
squeezed coherent state.

00:45:09.070 --> 00:45:12.720
So this is now the
state we have generated.

00:45:12.720 --> 00:45:18.170
And I explained to
you that such a state

00:45:18.170 --> 00:45:23.330
