coefficient goes to 1.

00:45:25.970 --> 00:45:31.500
So the squeezed vacuum is pretty
much transmitted without loss.

00:45:31.500 --> 00:45:34.200
But now, we have a very
strong local oscillator.

00:45:36.790 --> 00:45:40.000
Also, the reflection
coefficient goes to 0.

00:45:40.000 --> 00:45:43.830
We can just crank up the
