00:45:47.380 --> 00:45:48.890
reflected-- is n.

00:45:48.890 --> 00:45:53.130
So the limit we are looking at
it is small n and large alpha.

00:45:53.130 --> 00:45:55.960
But what we keep constant--
throughout actually

00:45:55.960 --> 00:45:59.390
all those questions-- is that
we have n photons in that beam.

