And I explained
to you in class--

00:46:06.690 --> 00:46:08.690
and I showed it to
you with operators--

00:46:08.690 --> 00:46:11.850
that this setup
is really creating

00:46:11.850 --> 00:46:16.430
the displeased squeezed vacuum.

00:46:16.430 --> 00:46:17.100
OK.

00:46:17.100 --> 00:46:20.790
Now, we have one
laser beam, which

00:46:20.790 --> 00:46:25.670
has an average value
of the field, alpha.

00:46:25.670 --> 00:46:26.770
It has certain properties.

00:46:29.700 --> 00:46:33.440
And now, I want to ask you, what
